Articles.Content:
I have tried installing B9 procedural wings on my ksp 1.8.1, but it keeps stopping at "verifying expansion: breaking grounds. I have had b9 aerospace before b9 procedural wings, and it worked fine. now, with b9 procedural wings uninstalled, it isnt working, and i am getting the same error. has anyone encountered this/know a solution to this? seeing as most of the crafts from kerbalx that I like have this mod, it would be great if it worked.

Edited January 23, 2020 by AguywithKSPproblems

That usually happens when some mod or dll is broken (you can see that above the loading bar if you have MM)

Otherwise, you could have unistalled a depency of a mod, what is your mod list?

Could you upload the KSP.log?
